reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Perfectly Acceptable Small Shelf
reviews.reviewText: Just as pictured. Metal frame quite sturdy; assembles easily. Printed fake-wood shelves look better than expected but will require care to avoid damage.
